<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6399682>
    dc:description "FIGURE 50. Pseudophasma amabile (Redtenbacher, 1906) comb. nov. A, B. Male, lectotype (NHMW), habitus in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views. C, D. Female, paralectotype (NHMW), habitus in dorsal (C) and lateral (D) views. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
